  "title": "SPA THERAPIST",
  "description": "<p>·  Deliver a variety of spa services (body treatments, massages, waxing and manicure/pedicure) in a safe and comfortable manner</p><p>· Maintain equipment and sample inventory of products</p><p>· Keep documentation and maintain clients’ files</p><p>· Keep a clean and stocked room</p><p>· Acknowledge and respond to relevant customer queries, needs and expectations</p><p>· Suggest and promote retail products or additional services</p><p>· Uphold hygiene standards and follow health and safety regulations</p><p>· Cooperate with and report on administration on any arising issues</p><p>· Apply best practices and be up to date with market trends</p><p>· Must work on public holidays and weekend</p>",
